  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time Lock VR 1 is an atmospheric first-person VR puzzle game where your main tool is <strong>Time Control</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a time agent trapped in a scientific experiment. Space and time are distorted, and to escape you’ll need to use unique abilities: slow down moving objects, rewind them to the past, or shift them across timelines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/673450/extras/cb091b5157cef9a6bb390464fe92c54a.poster.avif?t=1759325967\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/673450/extras/cb091b5157cef9a6bb390464fe92c54a.webm?t=1759325967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/673450/extras/cb091b5157cef9a6bb390464fe92c54a.mp4?t=1759325967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control time to solve puzzles: slow down, rewind, or shift objects between timelines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore environments where each location exists in different time periods.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with a fully immersive VR world: throw objects, open drawers, switch on lights, and uncover hidden details.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight enemies using special weapons and time-shift abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete mini-games and logic challenges built around temporal mechanics.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/673450/extras/be629f89e389ebdb1b5c9ceeedb2cc59.poster.avif?t=1759325967\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/673450/extras/be629f89e389ebdb1b5c9ceeedb2cc59.webm?t=1759325967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/673450/extras/be629f89e389ebdb1b5c9ceeedb2cc59.mp4?t=1759325967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Full time-control mechanics as the core of gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• A mix of puzzles, combat encounters, and mini-games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Sci-fi atmosphere: labs, portals, distorted spaces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Fully interactive VR environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Single-player VR experience for fans of puzzles and science fiction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >vr puzzle, time control, time manipulation, vr escape room, sci-fi vr, time travel game, time agent, vr investigation, logic puzzles vr, interactive vr world, singleplayer vr</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time Lock VR 1 is an atmospheric first-person VR puzzle game where your main tool is <strong>Time Control</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a time agent trapped in a scientific experiment. Space and time are distorted, and to escape you’ll need to use unique abilities: slow down moving objects, rewind them to the past, or shift them across timelines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/673450/extras/cb091b5157cef9a6bb390464fe92c54a.poster.avif?t=1759325967\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/673450/extras/cb091b5157cef9a6bb390464fe92c54a.webm?t=1759325967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/673450/extras/cb091b5157cef9a6bb390464fe92c54a.mp4?t=1759325967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control time to solve puzzles: slow down, rewind, or shift objects between timelines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore environments where each location exists in different time periods.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with a fully immersive VR world: throw objects, open drawers, switch on lights, and uncover hidden details.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight enemies using special weapons and time-shift abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete mini-games and logic challenges built around temporal mechanics.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic